---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Services" 
  description="Traditional Japanese landscaping, Ueki, Bonsai services, and garden design in South Bay LA."
>
  <!-- Services -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="services-content">
        <h1>Services</h1>
        
        <!-- Ueki -->
        <div class="service-section">
          <h2>Ueki 植木</h2>
          <p>Ueki is the centuries-old Japanese art of cultivating, shaping, and maintaining trees specifically for garden landscapes. Our Ueki services honor these traditional techniques while adapting to your unique environment.</p>
          
          <h3>What We Offer</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Tree selection and consultation for your climate and aesthetic goals</li>
            <li>Placement strategy for visual harmony and proper growing conditions</li>
            <li>Traditional Niwaki pruning and shaping to reveal natural tree architecture</li>
            <li>Cloud pruning (Tamamono) for pines and junipers</li>
            <li>Professional installation and transplanting</li>
            <li>Seasonal maintenance and care</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Species We Work With</h3>
          <p>Japanese Black Pine, Japanese White Pine, Japanese Maple, Flowering Cherry, Japanese Cedar, and other species suited to the South Bay LA climate.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Bonsai -->
        <div class="service-section">
          <h2>Bonsai 盆栽</h2>
          <p>Bonsai is more than small trees in pots - it's a living art form requiring patience, skill, and deep understanding of horticulture. Our Bonsai services range from beginner guidance to advanced styling.</p>
          
          <h3>What We Offer</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Custom Bonsai creation from nursery stock or collected material</li>
            <li>Styling and refinement using traditional and contemporary techniques</li>
            <li>Wiring for branch placement and movement</li>
            <li>Repotting and root work with proper timing and technique</li>
            <li>Care and maintenance services for your collection</li>
            <li>Education and training in Bonsai basics and advanced techniques</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h3>Bonsai Styles</h3>
          <p>We specialize in traditional styles including Formal Upright (Chokkan), Informal Upright (Moyogi), Slanting (Shakan), Cascade (Kengai), Semi-Cascade (Han-Kengai), and Literati (Bunjin).</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Garden Design -->
        <div class="service-section">
          <h2>Garden Design</h2>
          <p>Complete Japanese garden design and installation that honors traditional principles while creating spaces that function beautifully in modern settings. We work with your existing landscape or create new gardens from scratch.</p>
          
          <h3>What We Offer</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Initial consultation and site assessment</li>
            <li>Concept development and design plans</li>
            <li>Plant selection and procurement</li>
            <li>Hardscaping design (paths, stones, water features)</li>
            <li>Professional installation and project management</li>
            <li>Post-installation care guidance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Maintenance -->
        <div class="service-section">
          <h2>Maintenance</h2>
          <p>Japanese gardens and Bonsai collections require ongoing care to maintain their beauty and health. We offer maintenance services tailored to your specific needs, from seasonal visits to comprehensive care programs.</p>
          
          <h3>What We Offer</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Seasonal pruning and shaping</li>
            <li>Fertilization and soil care</li>
            <li>Pest and disease management</li>
            <li>Plant health monitoring</li>
            <li>Guidance on ongoing care practices</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .services-content {
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  
  .service-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xxl);
  }
  
  .service-section:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  
  .service-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  
  .service-section h3 {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  
  .service-section ul {
    margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-lg);
  }
  
  .service-section li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
  }
</style>
